10.15am Hello everyone to action from day 3 at Hobart. Australia dominated again yesterday but it was heartening to see some kind of fight from WI. Whether they can avoid the follow-on or not, we will have to wait and see, but they have done all they could do. Barring James Pattinson, who has lacked that penetration, all bowlers have done something and kept the batsmen honest. Will Steven Smith enforce the follow-on if the lead is close to 300?
